msgctxt "seo_title"
msgid "Common Voice and Hekaya Arts Initiative Kiswahili Writing Competition"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid ""
"Mozilla’s Common Voice in collaboration with Hekaya Arts Initiative is awarding the top three Kiswahili essay writers with prizes of $400 USD, $250 USD, and $100 USD respectively.\r"
"<br/>The writing competition is part of Mozilla’s Common Voice goal to grow Kiswahili’s open-source data set, enabling the inclusion of local African languages in tech use and development."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Mozilla’s <a id=\"a1\">Common Voice</a> in collaboration with Hekaya Arts Initiative is awarding the top three Kiswahili essay writers with prizes of $400 USD, $250 USD, and $100 USD respectively."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid ""
"The writing competition is part of Mozilla’s Common Voice goal to <a id=\"a1\">grow Kiswahili’s open-source data set</a>, enabling the inclusion of local African languages in tech use and "
"development."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Hekaya Arts Initiative is a literary and cultural organization, that facilitates conversations about the use and evolution of Kiswahili language through art and literary festivals."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid ""
"The competition seeks to attract submissions across different Kiswahili-speaking regions and diasporas, beyond East Africa where the language is predominantly spoken. The deadline is April 30, 2022,"
" and the winners will be announced on May 13, 2022."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Writers are encouraged to explore creative writing formats inspired by culture and social justice topics in the following categories:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Music/song, dance, and local instruments"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Language"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Culture and Heritage"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Cultural objects"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Beauty and aesthetics"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Housing/Architecture"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Indigenous health/traditional health practices"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Literature and Linguistics"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Traditional/historical livelihoods e.g. pottery"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Social issues such as land justice, mass graves, Christianity and its effects on cultural practices"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Local heroes/historical figures"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "History and archaeology"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Guidelines for submission"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Received submissions will be in the public domain. All work submitted will be under <a id=\"a1\">Public Domain (CC-0) license</a>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Participants must sign the Contributions Agreement template found <a id=\"a1\">here</a>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Text specifications:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "There should be no digits in the written work such as 2021; instead, use words"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "Abbreviations and acronyms like “USA” or “ICE” should be avoided because they may be read in a way that does not coincide with their spelling"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "The text should not use derogatory language"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "The text should not promote any form of gender harassment, abuse, or violence"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "The text should not perpetrate or condone sexual harassment or biases"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "The text should be respectful of gender diversities i.e. usage of correct pronouns"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "The text should not propagate violence and/or threats of violence"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "The text should be in a digital format not handwritten"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "The content must be your own, no plagiarized content"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.dcaac0e2-a409-4cd6-bcab-d52606f2f4e6"
msgid "All submissions should be sent to <a id=\"a1\">editor@hekaya.co.ke</a> by April 30, 2022. For more information visit, <a id=\"a2\">Hekaya Arts Initiative</a>."
msgstr ""

